New Posts All Forums: Forum Nav: [Official] Case Labs Owners Club Hi Everyone - I'm taking over this thread from Iamwardicus so PM me with questions. Please also make sure you're also on the official build log list here To get added, post in this thread with a pic of your case, preferably also include a link to your build log! For those who don't know - Aquaeros are non standard on their sizing and you may need this accessory in order to mount one: http://www.caselabs-store.com/flex-bay-5-25-device-mount-short-nonconforming/ Sig Link: [center][URL="http://www.overclock.net/computer-cases/940461-official-case-labs-owners-club.html#post12374637"]*Official* [B][COLOR="DeepSkyBlue"]CaseLabs[/COLOR][/B] Owners Club![/URL][/center] We'll also be having some votes for "best build" in each case.
